snippet.title: SpaceLab Simulator Trailer (2023)
snippet.description:
SpaceLab Simulator is an upcoming simulation game where you play as an independent contractor on the spaceship Adiona. 

You will deal with vexing situations, solve technical problems, make repairs and improvements, and submit daily reports to receive your revenue. Upgrade tools that will make your life and work easier, but before everything, try to keep your cargo safe.

Wishlist the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/619530

Follow the game to learn more:
Website: https://gelluloid.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Gelluloid
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/Gelluloid/
